This is an NTSC DVD compilation featuring the Nine Inch Nails&amp;#039; And All That Could Have Been television special. Full details on this special can be found here:  &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.nincollector.com/archive/releases/halo_17/17_d_vhs_tvcablepromo.htm&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.nincollector.com/archive/releases/halo_17/17_d_vhs_tvcablepromo.htm&lt;/a&gt; 

Also included are the full performance videos from the Still sessions (sourced from downloads from nin.com), the videos for We&amp;#039;re In This Together, Into The Void, Starsuckers, Inc., and Deep (2 versions). There&amp;#039;s also a few surprises. 

Almost all of the material included on this DVD was sourced from original VHS promos and transferred from an S-VHS VCR via S-Video to a miniDV camcorder then to PC via firewire for editing and mastering. Some of the material is from DVD sources. 

Enjoy, but don&amp;#039;t put this on ebay. I&amp;#039;m not your ATM. 

Special thanks goes out to leviathant, terryana, and hybridreplicate over at ETS for providing/lending source material to help make this possible
